    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.poster.avif?t=1728915907\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.webm?t=1728915907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/edc19a74683fe357847bdc3f1f3c446e.mp4?t=1728915907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个轻松的游戏中，你优化库存空间的能力将受到考验。每件遗物都有独特的形状和适应的挑战，使得游戏体验既有挑战性又充满成就感。当你发现隐藏的物品并不断完善策略以收集所有宝藏时，尽情享受那份成就感吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.poster.avif?t=1728915907\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.webm?t=1728915907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160710/extras/e827193932a1ea3803a48d890311b675.mp4?t=1728915907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有能力在《Loot Stack: Relics Hunter》中找到并整理所有的遗物吗？来测试你的技能，沉浸在一场难忘的中世纪冒险中吧！</p>",
